Product description

Complete manifold 171 mm, 232 bar, viton - Military Line

 

DESCRIPTION:

The set consists of two valves connected with an isolator.

The manifold is used to connect cylinders in a double-tank set (twinset). With the use of an isolator, it is possible to cut off the gas flow between the cylinders.

 

Valves and isolators in the Military Line version have been coated with HBC (Hard Black Coating) for increased resistance to damage.

 

Masking LVM (Low Visibility Marking)  is a low-visibility marking system used in special forces.

 

TECLINE MILITARY

It's a range of Tecline equipment designed in accordance with the specifications of various special forces and rescue teams.

The availability of Tecline Military products depends on the amount of production surpluses.

Check more: https://teclinediving.eu/military-line
